{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, I just can't recall it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found out later on that we did have Megillahs and Torahs at home and all sorts of Jewish artifacts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because later on, when we put all our things away and gave all our things to friends to keep for us while we were in the camps, and when we got them back, there were a lot of things like that that we did possess.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I just don't remember that we ever used them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- I had many friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would say that there probably was one or two amongst them who were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know quite how we found that they were, but generally not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was certainly not a Jewish area there and-- or a Jewish school or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very few Jews, I would say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we never talked about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- we only talked about school activities and sports, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But those were the good days, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were very happy in Heemstede.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, that I liked it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did well in, in the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember some of the friends from school have photographs of school, two friends in particular, who both had a birthday on the same day, 23rd of August, which I somehow always remember.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, I'm still in contact with those two boys from those days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you see them on the photograph, it's very strange because the one that, even in those days, [NON-ENGLISH], he had totally white hair.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other boy, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jurgen ?] Carmelo, he was a Negro.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We always called him a Negro.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, in those days, there was nothing wrong with [LAUGHS] calling him Negro.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
